Date: Tue, 24 Feb 2026 23:12:46 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: auto-generate meeting titles from transcript content

After summarization, meetings with auto-generated hash names (Meeting-XXXXXX)
now get a descriptive AI-generated title based on the summary content.

- Add generate_title() method to OllamaSummarizer (src/summarizer.py)
- Call title generation in process_recording when session name is a hash (simple_recorder.py)
- Fix meeting lookup in main.js to handle renamed meetings via audio file fallback
- User-provided names are never overwritten
- Title generation failure falls back silently to the original hash name
---
